<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Novo Contato - {{subject}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-top: 5px solid #3B82F6;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3B82F6;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3B82F6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .contact-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .field-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .field-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .field-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
        }
        .message-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .message-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3B82F6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .message-content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }
        .metadata {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .metadata h4 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .metadata-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 8px 0;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .metadata-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .metadata-value {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .actions {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6, #1D4ED8);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
        }
        .button.secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B7280, #4B5563);
        }
        .priority-indicator {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .priority-high {
            background-color: #FEE2E2;
            color: #EF4444;
        }
        .priority-normal {
            background-color: #DBEAFE;
            color: #3B82F6;
        }
        .priority-low {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            color: #6B7280;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #3B82F6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .timestamp {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .alert {
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            border: 1px solid #F59E0B;
            color: #92400E;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .alert.spam-warning {
            background-color: #FEE2E2;
            border-color: #EF4444;
            color: #991B1B;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .contact-info {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .button {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
            .metadata-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            .metadata-value {
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üíº Portfolio</div>
            <div class="subtitle">Novo Contato Recebido</div>
        </div>

        {{#if priority}}
        <div class="priority-indicator priority-{{priority}}">
            üìß Prioridade: {{priority}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="contact-info">
            <div class="contact-title">üìû Informa√ß√µes do Contato</div>
            
            <div class="field-group">
                <div class="field-label">Nome</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{name}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="field-group">
                <div class="field-label">E-mail</div>
                <div class="field-value">
                    <a href="mailto:{{email}}" style="color: white; text-decoration: underline;">
                        {{email}}
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="field-group">
                <div class="field-label">Assunto</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{subject}}</div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if phone}}
            <div class="field-group">
                <div class="field-label">Telefone</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{phone}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if company}}
            <div class="field-group">
                <div class="field-label">Empresa</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{company}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="message-section">
            <div class="message-title">üí¨ Mensagem</div>
            <div class="message-content">{{message}}</div>
        </div>

        {{#if spamWarning}}
        <div class="alert spam-warning">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Aviso de Spam</strong><br>
            Esta mensagem foi marcada como poss√≠vel spam. Verifique cuidadosamente antes de responder.
            <br><small>Raz√£o: {{spamReason}}</small>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if isImportant}}
        <div class="alert">
            <strong>‚≠ê Mensagem Importante</strong><br>
            Esta mensagem foi marcada como importante baseada no conte√∫do ou remetente.
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="metadata">
            <h4>üìä Informa√ß√µes T√©cnicas</h4>
            
            <div class="metadata-item">
                <span class="metadata-label">Data/Hora:</span>
                <span class="metadata-value">{{formatDate createdAt 'DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm:ss'}}</span>
            </div>
            
            {{#if ip}}
            <div class="metadata-item">
                <span class="metadata-label">IP do Remetente:</span>
                <span class="metadata-value">{{ip}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if location}}
            <div class="metadata-item">
                <span class="metadata-label">Localiza√ß√£o:</span>
                <span class="metadata-value">{{location.city}}, {{location.country}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if userAgent}}
            <div class="metadata-item">
                <span class="metadata-label">Navegador:</span>
                <span class="metadata-value">{{browser}} - {{device}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if referrer}}
            <div class="metadata-item">
                <span class="metadata-label">Origem:</span>
                <span class="metadata-value">{{referrer}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="metadata-item">
                <span class="metadata-label">ID da Mensagem:</span>
                <span class="metadata-value">{{id}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
            <a href="mailto:{{email}}?subject=Re: {{subject}}" class="button">
                üìß Responder
            </a>
            
            {{#if adminUrl}}
            <a href="{{adminUrl}}/contacts/{{id}}" class="button secondary">
                üëÄ Ver no Admin
            </a>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        {{#if autoResponse}}
        <div class="alert">
            <strong>ü§ñ Resposta Autom√°tica</strong><br>
            Uma resposta autom√°tica foi enviada para {{email}} confirmando o recebimento da mensagem.
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if relatedContacts}}
        <div class="metadata">
            <h4>üìù Contatos Relacionados</h4>
            <p>Este e-mail j√° entrou em contato {{relatedContacts}} vez(es) anteriormente.</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Esta mensagem foi enviada atrav√©s do formul√°rio de contato do seu portfolio.</p>
            
            <p>
                <a href="{{siteUrl}}">Visitar Site</a> | 
                <a href="{{adminUrl}}">√Årea Administrativa</a>
            </p>
            
            <div class="timestamp">
                Notifica√ß√£o gerada automaticamente em {{formatDate now 'DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm:ss'}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>